As a business manager, try to find out the weak areas where you can work to make more profit.

Firstly, I will go through a data exploration to identify most important features and to explore the intercorrelation between features. After that I apply data normalization between varialbes and conduct feature engineering, Finally, I will be applying different machine learning algorithms and evaluating their respective success to a cross-validated splitted train-test set

−1.0≤ρxy≤+1.0¶
